# Constant Improvement (Lightweight)

After each significant prompt:

| Outcome               | Action                                                     |
| --------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |
| Success + new pattern | Append one line to `patterns-that-work.md`                 |
| Failure               | Append to `postmortems.log` or `postmortem-{timestamp}.md` |
| Inefficiency noticed  | Add one anti-pattern row to agent-efficiency-context.mdc   |

**Do not** after every prompt: full post-mortem, research, multi-agent review. Reserve for weekly/monthly cadence.

**Cost guardrail**: Improvement activities &lt;10% of total. If exceeding, reduce cadence.

**Full protocol**: `developer-enhancement/CONTINUOUS_IMPROVEMENT.md`
